net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects
Class MuWorld

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.jmuserver.gs.muObjects.MuWorld

public class MuWorld
extends java.lang.Object

The class represents the entire MuOnline visible world.
Encapsulates all the players and objects, all the maps and gates.

Author:
Miki, Marcel

InitGates

public void InitGates()
Initialize the world gates. The gates are similar to wormholes, you enter one gate and warp to another one, somewhere in the world. Warping through gates is usually bidirectional.
